trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> or other server control is being moved within its own zone, or to another zone.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> evento se desencadena cuando una <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> o de otro control de servidor se mueve dentro de su propia zona o a otra zona.

trans-unit.source: This can occur both when a user drags a control, and when there is a programmatic move.
trans-unit.target: Esto puede ocurrir cuando un usuario arrastra un control y cuando se produce un movimiento mediante programación.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartMoving%2A> method, and it provides an opportunity to cancel the moving process before it is complete or to track the user action.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> evento es desencadenado por la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartMoving%2A> (método) y proporciona una oportunidad para cancelar el proceso de mover antes de que se completa o para realizar el seguimiento de la acción del usuario.

trans-unit.source: If the move is completed and the control placed in a new position, this event is followed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved> event.
trans-unit.target: Si se ha completado el movimiento y el control que se coloca en una nueva posición, este evento va seguido por el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs> class contains information about the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs> clase contiene información sobre la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> eventos.

trans-unit.source: It provides access to the Web Parts control that is being moved and the zone it is being moved to.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona acceso a lo controles de elementos Web que se va a mover y la zona se mueve a.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> or other server control being moved.
trans-unit.target: Control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> u otro control de servidor que se está moviendo.

trans-unit.source: The target <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase" /> to which <c>webPart</c> is being moved.
trans-unit.target: Elemento <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase" /> de destino al que se va a mover <c>webPart</c>.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the index of <c>webPart</c> relative to other controls within <c>zone</c>.
trans-unit.target: Entero que indica el índice de <c>webPart</c> con respecto a otros controles de <c>zone</c>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Web Parts zone to which the Web Parts control is being moved.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece la zona de elementos Web a la que se está desplazando el control de elementos Web.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase" /> to which the Web Parts control is being moved.
trans-unit.target: Zona <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase" /> a la que se desplaza el control de elementos Web.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the index position of a Web Parts control within its zone.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece la posición de índice de un control de elementos Web en su zona.

trans-unit.source: The numerical order of a control within its zone.
trans-unit.target: El orden numérico de un control dentro de su zona.

trans-unit.source: The first control in a zone has an index value of zero.
trans-unit.target: El primer control de una zona tiene un valor de índice cero.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs.ZoneIndex%2A> property indicates the numerical order (or ordinal position) within the zone for the Web Parts control being moved in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs.ZoneIndex%2A> propiedad indica el orden numérico (o la posición ordinal) dentro de la zona para el control de elementos Web que se mueven el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoving> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses this property to track and manage its collection of Web Parts controls on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control utiliza esta propiedad para realizar un seguimiento y administrar su colección de controles de elementos Web en una página Web.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs.ZoneIndex%2A> property for a control might not equal the index value for the same control within the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: El valor de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartMovingEventArgs.ZoneIndex%2A> propiedad para un control no podría igual al valor de índice para el mismo control en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A> colección.
